---
title: BBQ Chicken & Sweet Potato Bowls with Bachan’s® Original Japanese Barbecue Sauce, Ginger Rice & Chili Soy Mayo
description: Tonight, we’ve got a meal that’ll leave you feeling totally zen. This “Buddha bowl” is a one-bowl veggie meal that won’t disappoint. Here, Japanese BBQ-and-sesame-glazed sweet potatoes and mushrooms, roasted bell pepper, spicy soy mayo, and a scattering of sesame seeds are all served over a heap of fluffy, gingery rice. You’re one bite away from inner dinner peace.
